{"id":161893,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/明報-民運：浙江數千村民騷亂1438/","date":"2011-06-16T23:30:47Z","modified":"2011-06-17T05:46:14Z","title":"明報 | 民運：浙江數千村民騷亂","content":"<p>中國人權民運信息中心表示，浙江台州市一名村長，被油站職員打傷，引發數千名村民騷亂，數千名武警及公安到場維持秩序。</p>\n<div>\n<p>中心指，台州市開發區「日山份村」，因為附近土地開發，同開發商及企業就補助出現爭拗，村長周二下午到當地中石化加油站，商討提高補助金時，被油站職員毆打，數千名村民包圍油站，搬來大石封鎖附近道路。</p>\n<p>現場消息說，事件到周四早上仍未平息，當局調派數千名武警、特警及公安到場，實施戒嚴。</p>\n<p>(綜合)</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGltcHJlc3Npb24iLCAicHJvcGVydGllcyI6IHsidG9rZW4iOiAiYTRhNDYwYTM5MDRlZWU4ZmY1ZTAyNGVhNGJkZTdhYzIifX0=&amp;ip=1&amp;img=1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /><img src=\"http://pixel.quantserve.com/pixel/p-89EKCgBk8MZdE.gif\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" width=\"1\" height=\"1\" /><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://api.mixpanel.com/track/?data=eyJldmVudCI6ICJmdWxsdGV4dGNsaWNrIiwgInByb3BlcnRpZXMiOiB7InRva2VuIjogImE0YTQ2MGEzOTA0ZWVlOGZmNWUwMjRlYTRiZGU3YWMyIn19&amp;ip=1&amp;redirect=http://talkita.com/wrap?url=http%3A%2F%2Fmingpao.feedsportal.com%2Fc%2F33528%2Ff%2F585672%2Fs%2F15ec896d%2Fl%2F0Linews0Bmingpao0N0Chtm0CINews0C20A110A6160Cca41438a0Bhtm%2Fstory01.htm&amp;title=%E6%B0%91%E9%81%8B%EF%BC%9A%E6%B5%99%E6%B1%9F%E6%95%B8%E5%8D%83%E6%9D%91%E6%B0%91%E9%A8%B7%E4%BA%82%5B14%3A38%5D\">Chat about this story w/ Talkita</a></p>\n<p>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</p>\n<form action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\" method=\"POST\"> 定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=750556\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a></p></form>\n","author":1,"categories":[8779],"tags":[]}